To install ipfs in ubuntu, go to dist.ipfs.tech and download archive for go-ipfs.
Then decompress it. Enter to the folder and run sudo install.sh
To test run ipfs --version.
To initialize repo to store ipfs config, run sudo ipfs init.
This is where it will store its settings and internal data.
TO see id again type sudo ipfs id.
To enjoin your node to the world , run `ipfs daemon`
